name: TRIUMPH HERALD
description:
When I was little it always seemed scorching hot, and we also had a really old red car called a Triumph Herald. It would never start and we had to use a spanner to hit something in the engine to get it going. The spanner was kept in the ash tray. Ever since I was little I’ve always wanted to get one exactly the same (maybe minus the spanner :D)
Personal daily art story
Number 11 #STOREEZ by Cat Brown/ Treasvre Trove
